"instance and you will not be allowed to download it again."
msgstr ""

#: ../../aggregate-install.rst:495
msgid ""
"After creating the instance, add security rules for allowing both HTTP "
"and HTTPS. Choose the :guilabel:`Security Groups` tab and click on the "
"auto-created security group associated with your new instance. This might"
" have been called *launch-wizard-1*. If you’re not sure, you can go to "
"the Instances tab to see which Security Group is listed for the new "
